    public class PathfindToCoords
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.CommandGroup
    This function takes a Vector2 for a final destination, and uses the environment set in MapCreator to pathfind to the Vector2 It break and A* path into a series of line sgments and drives along those segments.
